msgstr "The wizard sets up a fresh installation. You'll need:"

msgid "setup.intro.req1.title"
msgstr "Microsoft 365 tenant with admin access"

msgid "setup.intro.req1.body"
msgstr "You'll need to create an app registration in Entra ID. Guide: <a href=\"https://github.com/ftrilloNL/neo-afk-oss/blob/main/docs/entra-id-setup.md\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"underline\">docs/entra-id-setup.md</a>. Note the Client ID, Tenant ID, and Client Secret."

