msgstr "Shared mailbox + licensed \"noreply\" mailbox"

msgid "setup.intro.req2.body"
msgstr "Shared calendar = shared mailbox (e.g. <code>vacation@…</code>). Mail sending = licensed mailbox (e.g. <code>noreply@…</code>) with auth-SMTP enabled. Details in <a href=\"https://github.com/ftrilloNL/neo-afk-oss/blob/main/docs/smtp-setup.md\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"underline\">docs/smtp-setup.md</a>."

